en_60346_0	Major General B.V.D.P Abeynayake assumed office as the 30th Adjutant General of the Army Headquarters on Thursday (16) during a simple ceremony.
en_60346_1	The new Adjutant General left his signature for an official document, amidst religious observances and symbolized the acceptance of the appointment.
en_60346_2	Staff officers of the Branch, officers and Other Ranks were present at the office.
en_60346_3	He succeeded Major General Nevil Weerasinghe who is to retire from the Army.
